text: Momen Uddin Ahmed is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Khulna-6. ==Career== Ahmed was elected to parliament from Khulna-6 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. He served as the State Minister of Power in the cabinet of President Hussain Mohammad Ershad. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:State Ministers of Power, Energy and Mineral Resources Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
